[Episode 29]

17
00:01:40,910 --> 00:01:43,000
What a useless fool she is.

18
00:01:43,800 --> 00:01:45,750
After all my years of careful nurture,

19
00:01:45,960 --> 00:01:48,270
she was pushed to the edge
by a young girl.

20
00:01:48,720 --> 00:01:49,800
She even wanted to cut off my hand

21
00:01:49,800 --> 00:01:51,720
and kneel to apologize to Liu Wencai.

22
00:01:52,000 --> 00:01:54,030
She must have gone mad.

23
00:01:57,520 --> 00:01:59,360
You dare to speak of nurturing us?

24
00:01:59,910 --> 00:02:00,910
Since we were young,

25
00:02:01,160 --> 00:02:02,190
you've always treated my sister and me

26
00:02:02,190 --> 00:02:03,830
as tools to gain power.

27
00:02:05,270 --> 00:02:06,800
If not for your careful nurture,

28
00:02:08,390 --> 00:02:09,390
would Shuran

29
00:02:10,640 --> 00:02:12,480
have gone mad?

30
00:02:13,200 --> 00:02:15,150
Do you even see me as your father?

31
00:02:15,270 --> 00:02:17,240
Do you even remember
that you're a father?

32
00:02:18,590 --> 00:02:19,640
Then you should do

33
00:02:19,640 --> 00:02:20,920
what a father should do.

34
00:02:20,960 --> 00:02:21,870
What do you mean?

35
00:02:22,080 --> 00:02:24,200
Write a letter to the emperor
and resign from your position.

36
00:02:24,550 --> 00:02:26,520
Say it's your fault
for not teaching your children well

37
00:02:26,870 --> 00:02:28,080
and that you're willing to become a monk

38
00:02:28,480 --> 00:02:31,800
and pray for the dead
to atone for your sins.

39
00:02:32,040 --> 00:02:33,270
Are you crazy?

40
00:02:33,760 --> 00:02:35,320
Why should I do that?

41
00:02:35,320 --> 00:02:36,670
To save Shuran.

42
00:02:37,040 --> 00:02:38,040
To save her,

43
00:02:38,240 --> 00:02:40,390
you're willing to abandon your father?

44
00:02:40,710 --> 00:02:42,430
You'll only stay
in the temple temporarily.

45
00:02:43,150 --> 00:02:44,080
After the dust has settled,

46
00:02:45,360 --> 00:02:47,710
I'll find a way to bring you back,

47
00:02:47,920 --> 00:02:50,040
and you can continue
your luxurious life.

48
00:02:50,320 --> 00:02:51,830
It's easy for you to say.

49
00:02:52,040 --> 00:02:53,390
This incident has caused
such a commotion.

50
00:02:53,760 --> 00:02:55,830
Who knows how long
I have to stay at the temple

51
00:02:55,830 --> 00:02:57,480
before things settle down?

52
00:03:02,960 --> 00:03:04,550
If you don't help her,

53
00:03:05,830 --> 00:03:09,360
you'll lose more than just a daughter.

54
00:03:10,920 --> 00:03:11,550
You...

55
00:03:22,710 --> 00:03:26,040
Old Madam, the medicine is ready.

56
00:03:26,830 --> 00:03:28,830
It will be delivered tonight
at the Hour of Xu.

57
00:03:31,830 --> 00:03:32,920
Everything

58
00:03:34,710 --> 00:03:36,360
is all my fault.

59
00:03:37,200 --> 00:03:38,870
I thought

60
00:03:39,480 --> 00:03:43,110
I managed the Jiang family well.

61
00:03:44,710 --> 00:03:48,590
But I still let the Ye family fall
into the Ji family's trap.

62
00:03:49,110 --> 00:03:50,550
Poor Zhenzhen left too early,

63
00:03:52,080 --> 00:03:55,430
leaving Li behind
is already pitiful enough.

64
00:03:56,640 --> 00:03:58,240
Yet, I didn't believe her.

65
00:04:00,150 --> 00:04:02,270
The claims of matricide and fratricide

66
00:04:03,990 --> 00:04:06,670
were thrown at her,

67
00:04:08,960 --> 00:04:11,150
which filled her with despair
and disappointment.

68
00:04:11,760 --> 00:04:12,960
Now that I think of it,

69
00:04:14,590 --> 00:04:15,960
it was absolutely absurd.

70
00:04:16,080 --> 00:04:18,830
Old Madam,
don't blame yourself too much.

71
00:04:19,440 --> 00:04:21,000
Back when Madam Ye was alive,

72
00:04:21,150 --> 00:04:22,560
Madam Ji was still an outsider.

73
00:04:23,270 --> 00:04:25,560
No matter how careful you were,

74
00:04:25,680 --> 00:04:27,390
you couldn't guard against outsiders.

75
00:04:27,390 --> 00:04:29,200
Don't comfort me.

76
00:04:30,230 --> 00:04:33,830
A mistake is a mistake.

77
00:04:34,880 --> 00:04:36,830
Old Madam, Second Lady is here.

78
00:04:45,200 --> 00:04:48,120
Li, you should get more rest.

79
00:04:54,000 --> 00:04:54,710
Grandmother,

80
00:04:56,440 --> 00:04:57,590
I want to know

81
00:04:58,470 --> 00:05:00,910
what will happen to Madam Ji?

82
00:05:01,470 --> 00:05:04,470
Your father and I have discussed it.

83
00:05:06,030 --> 00:05:07,320
We've prepared the medicine.

84
00:05:08,470 --> 00:05:10,590
It will be given to her later.

85
00:05:11,120 --> 00:05:11,680
All right.

86
00:05:13,270 --> 00:05:15,200
I can go and see her off.

87
00:05:16,520 --> 00:05:19,910
I have a few final words to say to her.

88
00:05:20,270 --> 00:05:21,590
At the Hour of Xu tonight,

89
00:05:23,120 --> 00:05:24,230
you can go then.

90
00:05:25,520 --> 00:05:26,790
Thank you, Grandmother.

91
00:05:30,150 --> 00:05:30,830
Li.

92
00:05:35,560 --> 00:05:36,390
Li.

93
00:05:37,030 --> 00:05:38,440
I've done you wrong.

94
00:05:38,640 --> 00:05:41,520
I know you've been wronged
all these years.

95
00:05:43,150 --> 00:05:46,120
Even though we found the real culprit,

96
00:05:46,710 --> 00:05:48,590
we still can't clear your name.

97
00:05:48,880 --> 00:05:50,000
But don't worry.

98
00:05:51,030 --> 00:05:53,270
If you ever need anything,

99
00:05:54,520 --> 00:05:56,350
the family will do its best to help you

100
00:05:57,120 --> 00:05:58,390
so long it's within its means.

101
00:06:01,000 --> 00:06:01,960
It doesn't matter anymore.

102
00:06:05,560 --> 00:06:07,640
Old Madam, Consort Li sent a message.

103
00:06:12,880 --> 00:06:15,390
Today, Official Li stepped down
from his position as an apology.

104
00:06:15,880 --> 00:06:17,880
He said that Ji Shuran's actions

105
00:06:17,880 --> 00:06:19,350
were not her wishes

106
00:06:19,760 --> 00:06:21,830
and that she was manipulated by others.

107
00:06:22,390 --> 00:06:24,150
But he is aware of the severity
of her sins,

108
00:06:24,590 --> 00:06:26,560
so he decides to become a monk
to pray for forgiveness.

109
00:06:27,150 --> 00:06:30,590
Her Highness pities Madam Ji
for being manipulated.

110
00:06:31,120 --> 00:06:34,030
Though her crimes are severe,
there are reasons behind them.

111
00:06:34,440 --> 00:06:37,830
So she asks Grand Chancellor Jiang
to spare Mrs. Jiang's life.

112
00:06:38,520 --> 00:06:39,320
