113
00:06:39,760 --> 00:06:42,000
do you not hear my words clearly?

114
00:06:42,440 --> 00:06:43,590
I heard them clearly.

115
00:06:53,500 --> 00:06:54,150
Li.

116
00:06:55,350 --> 00:06:56,500
Where are you going?

117
00:07:03,150 --> 00:07:04,550
It's such a good news.

118
00:07:05,420 --> 00:07:07,420
I must quickly tell Mother.

119
00:07:20,420 --> 00:07:21,670
Let her go.

120
00:07:21,910 --> 00:07:23,060
We've wronged her.

121
00:07:24,470 --> 00:07:25,710
We did do her wrong.

122
00:07:30,470 --> 00:07:31,180
Consort Li,

123
00:07:31,550 --> 00:07:32,620
the message has been delivered.

124
00:07:32,860 --> 00:07:34,620
Grand Chancellor Jiang has agreed.

125
00:07:34,860 --> 00:07:35,550
You may leave.

126
00:07:35,550 --> 00:07:35,940
Yes, Your Highness.

127
00:07:44,620 --> 00:07:45,550
Jiang Li.

128
00:07:56,260 --> 00:07:57,260
Ji Shuran,

129
00:08:00,820 --> 00:08:04,350
