148
00:08:47,470 --> 00:08:48,310
What are you doing here?

149
00:08:49,590 --> 00:08:51,230
I'm here to see you off
for the last time.

150
00:09:01,380 --> 00:09:02,500
Don't try to scare me.

151
00:09:04,990 --> 00:09:06,430
I am the Lady of the Jiang family.

152
00:09:06,620 --> 00:09:09,020
My son, Jiang Bingji,
is Grand Chancellor Jiang's eldest son.

153
00:09:09,540 --> 00:09:12,260
My sister is the current emperor's
favorite consort.

154
00:09:13,900 --> 00:09:15,110
I still have the Ji family.

155
00:09:16,020 --> 00:09:17,260
You can't touch me.

156
00:09:17,660 --> 00:09:19,110
Lady of the Jiang family?

157
00:09:21,500 --> 00:09:22,740
Have you forgotten

158
00:09:23,620 --> 00:09:25,190
how you got your position

159
00:09:25,590 --> 00:09:27,190
in the first place?

160
00:09:27,350 --> 00:09:28,350
What do you mean?

161
00:09:28,540 --> 00:09:30,020
Aunt Hu told me everything.

162
00:09:30,780 --> 00:09:32,620
I heard Ji Shuran telling Ms. Sun

163
00:09:33,620 --> 00:09:35,380
that the physician who treated Madam Ye

164
00:09:35,380 --> 00:09:36,310
had returned to the capital

165
00:09:36,660 --> 00:09:38,070
and needed to be silenced.

166
00:09:38,350 --> 00:09:38,990
Silenced?

167
00:09:41,430 --> 00:09:44,110
Are you saying my mother didn't die
from being weak

168
00:09:44,110 --> 00:09:45,540
after giving birth to me?

169
00:09:45,830 --> 00:09:48,140
Even if she was weak,
she could still recuperate slowly.

170
00:09:49,140 --> 00:09:50,230
By the end of her confinement,

171
00:09:50,710 --> 00:09:53,350
her health was improving.

172
00:09:54,020 --> 00:09:55,620
Then suddenly, her condition worsened

173
00:09:56,020 --> 00:09:57,260
and she didn't last six months.

174
00:09:58,540 --> 00:09:59,590
Thinking back,

175
00:10:00,230 --> 00:10:01,660
it's possible that Ji Shuran bribed

176
00:10:01,660 --> 00:10:03,020
the physician who treated Madam Ye

177
00:10:03,590 --> 00:10:05,540
to tamper with her medicine.

178
00:10:06,860 --> 00:10:08,540
That wretched woman.

179
00:10:09,540 --> 00:10:11,230
