I'll teach her a lesson.

182
00:10:18,260 --> 00:10:19,350
If you want,

183
00:10:20,470 --> 00:10:21,710
I can send you to meet her.

184
00:10:23,500 --> 00:10:24,070
What?

185
00:10:24,430 --> 00:10:27,950
Aunt Hu went to see her daughter.

186
00:10:28,900 --> 00:10:31,230
Before leaving, she left me a letter

187
00:10:31,710 --> 00:10:33,860
accusing you of poisoning my mother.

188
00:10:34,660 --> 00:10:35,190
Do you want

189
00:10:35,590 --> 00:10:37,660
to go to hell to settle this with her?

190
00:10:47,190 --> 00:10:49,310
Someone! I want
to see Grand Chancellor Jiang!

191
00:10:49,620 --> 00:10:50,350
Open this door!

192
00:10:50,740 --> 00:10:51,780
No point shouting for help.

193
00:10:52,900 --> 00:10:53,500
Ji Shuran,

194
00:10:54,540 --> 00:10:57,110
Grandmother and Father used
to care for you

195
00:10:57,620 --> 00:10:59,710
because you had lost a child.

196
00:11:00,350 --> 00:11:01,740
But now it's clear

197
00:11:03,020 --> 00:11:03,950
that your misery

198
00:11:04,620 --> 00:11:06,430
was all part of a plot you orchestrated.

199
00:11:08,590 --> 00:11:09,430
You're also aware

200
00:11:11,350 --> 00:11:13,830
that sacrificing lives
allows you to gain trust.

201
00:11:14,470 --> 00:11:16,900
Now, your retribution has arrived.

202
00:11:17,350 --> 00:11:18,380
Those who died unjustly

203
00:11:19,190 --> 00:11:20,310
are restless.

204
00:11:20,780 --> 00:11:21,860
They want to seek justice.

205
00:11:22,350 --> 00:11:23,860
Even in death, they won't let you off.

206
00:11:24,310 --> 00:11:25,740
You can't beat them, Ji Shuran.

207
00:11:26,780 --> 00:11:29,620
Remember this. From today,

208
00:11:30,430 --> 00:11:33,020
no one in the Jiang family
will believe you again.

209
00:11:33,430 --> 00:11:33,860
Jiang Li,

210
00:11:34,710 --> 00:11:36,110
even if I become a ghost,
I won't let you off.

211
00:11:36,380 --> 00:11:38,190
I won't let you off even
when I become a ghost.

212
00:11:39,110 --> 00:11:40,350
Fine, go and find her then.

213
00:11:41,260 --> 00:11:43,190
When you meet Jiang Li
in the underworld,

214
00:11:44,070 --> 00:11:45,660
she'll be the first to come after you.

215
00:11:46,230 --> 00:11:48,470
What... What did you say?

216
00:11:50,620 --> 00:11:51,020
You...

217
00:11:54,380 --> 00:11:55,350
You're not Jiang Li.

218
00:11:56,740 --> 00:11:57,740
Do you know

219
00:11:58,660 --> 00:11:59,860
how much Jiang Li suffered

220
00:12:01,470 --> 00:12:03,990
in Zhennyu Hall over these ten years?

221
00:12:04,830 --> 00:12:06,660
She was supposed
to be doted on by Father

222
00:12:07,020 --> 00:12:08,830
and a carefree daughter
of a noble family.

223
00:12:09,620 --> 00:12:10,380
But what happened?

224
00:12:13,140 --> 00:12:16,190
You not only caused her mother's death,

225
00:12:17,260 --> 00:12:18,830
but you also tarnished her reputation

226
00:12:19,500 --> 00:12:20,660
and sent her away.

227
00:12:21,310 --> 00:12:23,140
You handed her over to those people,

228
00:12:23,990 --> 00:12:25,590
letting her be tortured to death,

229
00:12:25,950 --> 00:12:27,190
tortured to death while still alive!

230
00:12:27,190 --> 00:12:28,020
Ji Shuran,

231
00:12:28,780 --> 00:12:30,110
do you understand that pain?

232
00:12:30,500 --> 00:12:31,380
Do you?

233
00:12:31,740 --> 00:12:33,190
Do you deserve forgiveness?

234
00:12:34,950 --> 00:12:38,110
