Consort Li has spoken.

262
00:14:33,260 --> 00:14:34,380
So no one will harm her.

263
00:14:36,540 --> 00:14:37,660
I only want to know

264
00:14:38,860 --> 00:14:40,950
when she fed me poison,

265
00:14:42,260 --> 00:14:44,990
did she feel even a bit
of reluctance and pity?

266
00:15:27,140 --> 00:15:28,660
How is she now?

267
00:15:29,990 --> 00:15:30,780
She has gone mad.

268
00:15:35,500 --> 00:15:36,620
