270
00:15:41,830 --> 00:15:43,070
Since she has gone mad,

271
00:15:45,020 --> 00:15:46,470
let her guard the tomb.

272
00:15:48,230 --> 00:15:52,710
Let her experience
what Aunt Hu suffered.

273
00:15:59,380 --> 00:16:00,260
Li,

274
00:16:03,260 --> 00:16:05,020
do you hate me?

275
00:16:07,740 --> 00:16:08,860
