day by day,

279
00:16:22,020 --> 00:16:24,620
I thought she was in poor health.

280
00:16:26,350 --> 00:16:30,070
I never thought
she was being harmed by someone.

281
00:16:31,470 --> 00:16:32,710
If I had known,

282
00:16:33,950 --> 00:16:35,740
I would never have let Ji Shuran set foot

283
00:16:35,740 --> 00:16:37,470
at the Jiang family's gates.

284
00:16:42,310 --> 00:16:45,620
I shouldn't even have accused you
of matricide and fratricide,

285
00:16:46,110 --> 00:16:48,380
neglecting you for ten years

286
00:16:49,540 --> 00:16:50,380
and

287
00:16:51,430 --> 00:16:53,660
almost causing you to lose your life.

288
00:16:54,260 --> 00:16:57,620
Li, do you still resent me

289
00:16:58,380 --> 00:17:00,380
about the evil spirit incident?

290
00:17:01,380 --> 00:17:02,380
I don't hate you.

291
00:17:06,150 --> 00:17:07,300
I've forgiven you.

292
00:17:10,950 --> 00:17:11,710
Li.

293
00:17:13,950 --> 00:17:14,670
Father.

294
00:17:16,100 --> 00:17:17,100
If you want to hear

295
00:17:18,230 --> 00:17:19,060
such words,

296
00:17:21,630 --> 00:17:23,150
I can say them to you.

297
00:17:27,430 --> 00:17:28,500
But do you think

298
00:17:30,780 --> 00:17:31,710
it's possible?

299
00:17:34,300 --> 00:17:35,820
You can't even imagine

300
00:17:36,020 --> 00:17:38,100
what Li went through in Zhennyu Hall.

301
00:17:41,190 --> 00:17:41,950
Over those ten years,

302
00:17:41,950 --> 00:17:43,500
Li had to fetch water, cook,

303
00:17:43,670 --> 00:17:44,820
do laundry, and mend clothes.

304
00:17:46,150 --> 00:17:47,990
Li has endure hunger, cold,

305
00:17:48,340 --> 00:17:49,150
falling down,

306
00:17:51,260 --> 00:17:53,630
and live under constant scrutiny.

307
00:17:55,670 --> 00:17:57,340
Every day, I hoped for my family
to come and fetch me.

308
00:17:57,780 --> 00:17:59,190
Even just a letter.

309
00:17:59,950 --> 00:18:04,190
But there was nothing,
absolutely nothing.

310
00:18:06,020 --> 00:18:07,740
So I gradually lost hope

311
00:18:08,950 --> 00:18:11,580
[Kindness Beyond Reproach]
and felt completely abandoned.

312
00:18:15,780 --> 00:18:17,020
I wanted to return to the Jiang family

313
00:18:17,820 --> 00:18:19,540
and tried hard for it.

314
00:18:20,430 --> 00:18:25,060
But even that wish couldn't be fulfilled.

315
00:18:33,710 --> 00:18:34,500
Li...

316
00:18:46,630 --> 00:18:47,260
Father,

317
00:18:50,300 --> 00:18:51,670
why don't you tell me?

318
00:18:52,780 --> 00:18:53,990
Tell me

319
00:18:54,740 --> 00:18:56,780
how to heal the scars left

320
00:18:58,190 --> 00:18:59,470
over these ten years?

321
00:19:01,340 --> 00:19:02,990
Only the wounds may heal.

322
00:19:03,870 --> 00:19:05,870
But scars will always remain.

323
00:19:06,670 --> 00:19:10,820
One's actions lead to consequences,
resulting in family discord.

324
00:19:12,230 --> 00:19:13,260
Your Li

325
00:19:14,150 --> 00:19:15,630
can't come back.

326
00:19:34,820 --> 00:19:38,300
You... You're not attending
court anymore?

327
00:19:43,100 --> 00:19:47,060
Ruoyao has been making a ruckus
on seeing her mother lately.

328
00:19:47,300 --> 00:19:49,670
I want to take her away
from the capital for a few days

329
00:19:50,540 --> 00:19:51,430
to ease things.

330
00:19:52,430 --> 00:19:54,670
And what about Li?

331
00:19:54,780 --> 00:19:55,910
Let her do as she wishes.

332
00:19:57,190 --> 00:19:59,990
Let Ji Shuran guard the tomb.

333
00:20:00,630 --> 00:20:02,300
Won't you stay in the capital?

334
00:20:04,060 --> 00:20:08,300
Now is the best time for you and Li
to mend your relationship...

335
00:20:08,630 --> 00:20:12,390
Mother, maybe if I distance myself a bit

336
00:20:13,390 --> 00:20:15,470
and don't interfere with Li's affairs,

337
00:20:16,740 --> 00:20:18,820
that's probably what she truly wants.

338
00:20:19,950 --> 00:20:20,870
Fine.

339
00:20:25,740 --> 00:20:28,470
Congratulations on your great victory,
Your Highness!

340
00:20:30,710 --> 00:20:34,260
Our soldiers have achieved much
in this expedition.

341
00:20:34,870 --> 00:20:37,150
We'll have a hearty celebration tonight!

342
00:20:37,470 --> 00:20:38,060
- Hail to Lord Cheng!
- Hail to Lord Cheng!

343
00:20:38,340 --> 00:20:38,990
- Hail to Lord Cheng!
- Hail to Lord Cheng!

344
00:20:39,260 --> 00:20:39,820
Drink up!

345
00:20:46,910 --> 00:20:48,100
All right. You can leave now.

346
00:20:48,100 --> 00:20:48,710
- Yes, Your Highness.
- Yes, Your Highness.

347
00:21:04,820 --> 00:21:05,820
My sister

348
00:21:07,190 --> 00:21:08,430
is too useless.

349
00:21:08,630 --> 00:21:09,870
Although we lost
the Office of Imperial Diviner,

350
00:21:10,780 --> 00:21:11,910
there were unexpected gains.

351
00:21:12,740 --> 00:21:13,540
The Ji family has fallen

352
00:21:13,820 --> 00:21:15,430
and the Jiang family
has paid a heavy price.

353
00:21:15,910 --> 00:21:17,230
Jiang Yuanbai was severely affected
by the setback

354
00:21:17,910 --> 00:21:18,910
and took leave from court.

355
00:21:19,230 --> 00:21:21,430
That means our people

356
00:21:22,470 --> 00:21:24,300
are dominating my brother's court now.

357
00:21:26,820 --> 00:21:27,780
[Prosperous Era]
Since there are no issues,

358
00:21:28,340 --> 00:21:29,190
let's adjourn.

359
00:21:30,100 --> 00:21:30,950
Your Majesty,

360
00:21:31,710 --> 00:21:32,870
Lord Cheng

361
00:21:32,870 --> 00:21:35,020
has reclaimed significant territory
in the north for Yan.

362
00:21:35,430 --> 00:21:36,740
The emperor of Dai Country
has retreated ten li

363
00:21:36,740 --> 00:21:38,190
beyond the northern border.

364
00:21:38,540 --> 00:21:40,580
The people in the northern border town
are also settled.

365
00:21:40,710 --> 00:21:42,540
Such great news
is worthy of celebration.

366
00:21:42,710 --> 00:21:44,430
Let's reward Lord Cheng,

367
00:21:44,500 --> 00:21:47,100
to boost the soldier's morale
who serve the country and the people.

368
00:21:48,150 --> 00:21:51,470
What should I reward him, Official Li?

369
00:21:51,950 --> 00:21:53,020
While Dai Country is retreating,

370
00:21:53,740 --> 00:21:55,820
they still harbor ill intentions
toward Yan.

371
00:21:56,100 --> 00:21:58,100
Add troops
and reinforce Lord Cheng's strength

372
00:21:58,260 --> 00:21:59,740
to fortify our northern borders

373
00:22:00,020 --> 00:22:01,260
and deter the Dai Country.

374
00:22:01,820 --> 00:22:03,060
What do all of you think?

375
00:22:03,230 --> 00:22:04,780
I agree.

376
00:22:04,910 --> 00:22:07,580
I second the motion.

377
00:22:08,710 --> 00:22:13,260
- I second the motion.
- I second the motion.

378
00:22:19,540 --> 00:22:20,780
Such a hateful play!

379
00:22:24,100 --> 00:22:26,230
Those ministers have become
Lord Cheng's supporters.

380
00:22:26,630 --> 00:22:27,670
With Jiang Yuanbai absent,

381
00:22:27,780 --> 00:22:29,340
only Li Zhongnan's supporters remain.

382
00:22:29,340 --> 00:22:30,260
Your Majesty, calm down.

383
00:22:30,630 --> 00:22:31,990
Lord Cheng's military achievements
are impressive

384
00:22:32,150 --> 00:22:33,740
and the court is inevitably wary.

385
00:22:34,630 --> 00:22:36,580
Your Majesty, you must not lose
your composure now,

386
00:22:36,870 --> 00:22:38,230
or it will cause unrest
among the people.

387
00:22:38,540 --> 00:22:39,780
I am well aware of this.

388
00:22:39,780 --> 00:22:41,230
But it's hard not to be angry.

389
00:22:41,340 --> 00:22:42,820
Lord Cheng has his own plans.

390
00:22:43,100 --> 00:22:44,630
How do we know
we can't strategize as well?

391
00:22:45,060 --> 00:22:46,230
I have just received intelligence

392
00:22:46,470 --> 00:22:49,150
that the internal strife
in Great Zhao is about to end.

393
00:22:49,630 --> 00:22:51,340
Has the prince
of Great Zhao taken control?

394
00:22:51,740 --> 00:22:52,300
Yes.

395
00:22:52,910 --> 00:22:54,340
The situation
in Great Zhao is stabilizing.

396
00:22:54,740 --> 00:22:56,020
The prince of Great Zhao

397
00:22:56,300 --> 00:22:57,820
has successfully ascended to the throne.

398
00:22:58,230 --> 00:23:00,390
To prevent the remnants
of the rebel forces from rising again,

399
00:23:00,710 --> 00:23:02,150
he now needs

400
00:23:02,430 --> 00:23:04,020
a reliable ally.

401
00:23:04,430 --> 00:23:06,430
If we have such an ally in the south,

402
00:23:06,670 --> 00:23:08,390
the additional troops Lord Cheng
has gathered

403
00:23:08,870 --> 00:23:10,230
are thus insignificant.

404
00:23:10,580 --> 00:23:13,670
How can you ensure he will ally with us?

405
00:23:13,950 --> 00:23:16,470
The young emperor
of Great Zhao has no heirs,

406
00:23:16,740 --> 00:23:17,910
only a younger sister.

407
00:23:18,230 --> 00:23:20,300
She fled to Great Yan during the chaos

408
00:23:20,500 --> 00:23:21,780
and was saved by us in the south.

409
00:23:22,150 --> 00:23:23,670
She has been in Great Yan since then.

410
00:23:23,780 --> 00:23:24,820
Prepare for a rainy day?

411
00:23:27,540 --> 00:23:28,150
Good.

412
00:23:28,500 --> 00:23:30,100
Congratulate the new emperor
of Great Zhao on his ascension.

413
00:23:30,580 --> 00:23:32,100
Also, invite the Great Zhao delegation

414
00:23:32,230 --> 00:23:33,870
to Great Yan
to discuss forming an alliance.

415
00:23:34,060 --> 00:23:35,780
This must be done grandly

416
00:23:35,950 --> 00:23:38,710
to show the world our good relations
with Great Zhao.

417
00:23:39,020 --> 00:23:40,670
I will handle it immediately.

418
00:23:42,100 --> 00:23:42,540
By the way,

419
00:23:43,580 --> 00:23:44,630
for such an important event,

420
00:23:44,910 --> 00:23:46,950
it was usually managed
by Secretariat Director, Jiang Yuanbai

421
00:23:46,950 --> 00:23:48,780
along with the Ministry of Rites
and the Court for Dependencies.

422
00:23:49,060 --> 00:23:50,430
With Jiang on leave

423
00:23:51,060 --> 00:23:53,580
and the Secretary of the Ministry
of Rites elevated by Li Zhongnan,

424
00:23:54,300 --> 00:23:56,540
it might cause issues in the alliance
if we fully trust them.

425
00:23:56,710 --> 00:23:58,150
Do you have
a suitable candidate in mind?

426
00:23:58,340 --> 00:23:59,820
Since you asked,

427
00:24:00,230 --> 00:24:02,470
you must have someone in mind already.

428
00:24:03,470 --> 00:24:05,910
What do you think of Shen Yurong?

429
00:24:06,190 --> 00:24:07,190
He is quite capable.

430
00:24:08,260 --> 00:24:10,100
But you must be aware of his background.

431
00:24:10,740 --> 00:24:12,020
So do you think

432
00:24:12,580 --> 00:24:14,100
your pawn will give up

433
00:24:14,470 --> 00:24:17,060
the chance to approach Shen Yurong?

434
00:24:17,870 --> 00:24:19,740
Are you putting that pawn

435
00:24:20,300 --> 00:24:21,500
in danger?

436
00:24:21,670 --> 00:24:23,150
Are you worried she will be in danger?

437
00:24:23,390 --> 00:24:25,670
If a pawn enters a perilous situation,

438
00:24:26,060 --> 00:24:28,100
it becomes useless to us.

439
00:24:30,260 --> 00:24:31,390
In the past,

440
00:24:32,020 --> 00:24:33,630
you were the most ruthless at chess.

441
00:24:34,540 --> 00:24:36,150
You taught me to sacrifice one piece

442
00:24:36,910 --> 00:24:37,990
to save the game.

443
00:24:38,990 --> 00:24:41,190
Why hesitate now?

444
00:24:41,540 --> 00:24:42,820
Just want to use resources
to their fullest potential.

445
00:24:43,300 --> 00:24:43,950
Xiao Heng,

446
00:24:46,470 --> 00:24:47,670
are you getting
your emotions involved in this?

447
00:24:48,100 --> 00:24:48,740
No, I am not.

448
00:24:57,300 --> 00:24:58,820
You better not be.

449
00:25:12,190 --> 00:25:13,630
Have you found Situ Jiuyue yet?

450
00:25:13,670 --> 00:25:15,300
My Lord, why are you
so determined to find her?

451
00:25:15,390 --> 00:25:17,300
Last time, she got angry with you
for no reason

452
00:25:17,300 --> 00:25:19,340
and drank all the liquor
in the Duke's Residence.

453
00:25:19,670 --> 00:25:20,260
My Lord,

454
00:25:20,430 --> 00:25:21,990
I mean Situ Jiuyue likes to disappear

455
00:25:21,990 --> 00:25:23,540
into the deep mountains and forests.

456
00:25:23,870 --> 00:25:25,820
She won't come out
for ten days or even half a month

457
00:25:26,100 --> 00:25:27,910
unless she finds
the medicinal herbs she's looking for.

458
00:25:27,910 --> 00:25:28,950
Send more people.

459
00:25:29,260 --> 00:25:31,500
We must find her
before the Great Zhao delegation arrives.

460
00:25:32,150 --> 00:25:32,540
Yes, My Lord.

461
00:25:36,340 --> 00:25:37,190
Your Highness,

462
00:25:37,950 --> 00:25:39,060
our agents have received information

463
00:25:39,540 --> 00:25:41,870
that the Great Zhao delegation
is coming to Great Yan.

464
00:25:42,300 --> 00:25:43,340
Great Zhao
has accepted their invitation.

465
00:25:43,710 --> 00:25:44,870
When the two nations form an alliance,

466
00:25:45,100 --> 00:25:46,870
the emperor of Great Zhao
will personally lead the delegation.

467
00:25:48,740 --> 00:25:50,780
The alliance between Great Zhao
and Great Yan

468
00:25:50,870 --> 00:25:52,390
is a variable for us.

469
00:25:53,670 --> 00:25:54,390
Any strategy?

470
00:25:54,990 --> 00:25:56,300
The alliance is not unexpected.

471
00:25:57,020 --> 00:25:58,260
But they are coming too quickly.

472
00:25:59,100 --> 00:25:59,780
What do you mean?

473
00:26:00,340 --> 00:26:01,430
During the previous internal strife
in Great Zhao,

474
00:26:01,580 --> 00:26:03,020
the princess of Great Zhao fled
to Great Yan.

475
00:26:03,780 --> 00:26:05,230
The main purpose

476
00:26:05,230 --> 00:26:06,300
of the emperor coming personally

477
00:26:06,670 --> 00:26:07,740
is to bring the princess back.

478
00:26:08,870 --> 00:26:10,950
Zhao Ye has probably found
this princess.

479
00:26:11,430 --> 00:26:12,430
That's why the emperor
of Great Zhao makes haste

480
00:26:12,430 --> 00:26:14,670
to come with the delegation in person.

481
00:26:14,820 --> 00:26:17,470
It's both a blessing and a curse.

482
00:26:18,230 --> 00:26:20,340
If the princess of Great Zhao dies

483
00:26:20,340 --> 00:26:21,950
in Great Yan,

484
00:26:23,230 --> 00:26:26,710
that brother of mine will be in trouble.

485
00:26:28,340 --> 00:26:30,190
Go and keep a close watch on Xiao Heng.

486
00:26:30,630 --> 00:26:32,630
Investigate everyone he comes
into contact with.

487
00:26:34,020 --> 00:26:34,580
Yes, Your Highness.

488
00:26:42,820 --> 00:26:44,630
[Taiji Hall]
Mr. Shen, you've completed your duties.

489
00:26:44,630 --> 00:26:46,870
This time, you are also
in charge of welcoming the delegation,

490
00:26:47,100 --> 00:26:49,300
which shows
the emperor's deep trust in you.

491
00:26:49,300 --> 00:26:51,020
Your future is indeed bright.

492
00:26:51,150 --> 00:26:53,230
It is indeed worth celebrating.

493
00:26:53,430 --> 00:26:55,670
My son is not very talented
but has some knowledge of music.

494
00:26:55,870 --> 00:26:58,870
Could he play the flute and qin
at the banquet as a gift

495
00:26:59,060 --> 00:27:01,190
for the alliance
between the two nations?

496
00:27:01,300 --> 00:27:03,540
I am merely doing my duty for the court.

497
00:27:04,020 --> 00:27:05,630
I cannot be compared to you all.

498
00:27:05,740 --> 00:27:07,670
As for the talents needed
to receive the delegation,

499
00:27:07,950 --> 00:27:09,670
I will compile a list according
to the specifications required

500
00:27:09,780 --> 00:27:10,580
by the Ministry of Rites

501
00:27:10,990 --> 00:27:12,260
and arrange everything accordingly.

502
00:27:12,740 --> 00:27:14,670
Those who wish to contribute

503
00:27:14,670 --> 00:27:16,500
are welcome to submit their names.

504
00:27:16,630 --> 00:27:19,340
Thank you in advance, Mr. Shen.

505
00:27:21,100 --> 00:27:21,860
- I shall take my leave.
- I shall get going.

506
00:27:22,340 --> 00:27:22,910
I'll take my leave now.

507
00:27:24,820 --> 00:27:28,540
Mr. Shen, the arrangements
for this grand alliance are extensive.

508
00:27:29,100 --> 00:27:30,100
Take care of yourself.

509
00:27:30,670 --> 00:27:31,510
If you need anything,

510
00:27:31,620 --> 00:27:33,510
I will do my best to help.

511
00:27:33,620 --> 00:27:34,190
Thank you.

512
00:27:43,260 --> 00:27:44,190
[Ye's Residence]

513
00:27:44,190 --> 00:27:44,950
Eat more.

514
00:27:46,270 --> 00:27:46,950
Eat more.

515
00:27:47,540 --> 00:27:48,380
All you do is eat.

516
00:27:48,540 --> 00:27:49,470
Is that all you do?

517
00:27:49,990 --> 00:27:51,190
Li is already so thin.

518
00:27:51,300 --> 00:27:53,190
As her brother, can't you advise her?

519
00:27:53,300 --> 00:27:55,300
You know what Li's temper is like.

520
00:27:55,620 --> 00:27:57,710
Besides, I'm not her only brother.

521
00:27:58,620 --> 00:27:59,990
Why aren't you scolding Ye Shijie too?

522
00:28:03,140 --> 00:28:05,510
The court is selecting people
to welcome the Great Zhao delegation

523
00:28:05,860 --> 00:28:07,860
and perform at the banquet.

524
00:28:08,750 --> 00:28:11,270
With Li's skills,
she will surely be chosen.

525
00:28:11,510 --> 00:28:12,990
Maybe finding something for her to do

526
00:28:13,430 --> 00:28:14,820
will help her feel better.

527
00:28:15,670 --> 00:28:17,470
But I don't know
if she wants to participate.

528
00:28:17,860 --> 00:28:19,270
I'll be counting on both of you

529
00:28:19,670 --> 00:28:20,710
to persuade her.

530
00:28:28,670 --> 00:28:30,540
Let's eat together.

531
00:28:35,140 --> 00:28:36,820
What... What did you say?

532
00:28:37,060 --> 00:28:38,620
He said he wants you to join him.

533
00:28:42,380 --> 00:28:43,820
Here, eat some.

534
00:28:44,300 --> 00:28:44,750
All right.

535
00:28:45,230 --> 00:28:46,470
Everything will be fine.

536
00:28:51,860 --> 00:28:52,430
Li.

537
00:28:55,030 --> 00:28:56,820
The Great Zhao delegation will arrive
in a few days.

538
00:28:57,470 --> 00:28:58,820
The court is selecting people
to welcome them.

539
00:28:59,540 --> 00:29:00,580
Are you interested?

540
00:29:01,270 --> 00:29:02,950
I just heard Jingrui and Liu Xu say

541
00:29:03,540 --> 00:29:04,510
they will participate.

542
00:29:04,990 --> 00:29:05,820
If you are chosen,

543
00:29:05,950 --> 00:29:07,270
our team can be together again.

544
00:29:09,380 --> 00:29:12,300
No, I just want to rest for now.

545
00:29:12,670 --> 00:29:13,340
After this, I want you,

546
00:29:18,300 --> 00:29:20,430
Liu Xu, and Jiang Jingrui

547
00:29:20,990 --> 00:29:22,100
not to come and see me.

548
00:29:22,820 --> 00:29:23,470
I want peace.

549
00:29:39,470 --> 00:29:40,100
Zhao.

550
00:29:42,670 --> 00:29:46,030
