00:33:10,300 --> 00:33:11,100
It's me.

579
00:33:15,030 --> 00:33:16,470
I'm Xue Fangfei.

580
00:33:20,140 --> 00:33:20,670
Haitang.

581
00:33:23,710 --> 00:33:24,820
Madam.

582
00:33:25,470 --> 00:33:26,060
It's me.

583
00:33:33,860 --> 00:33:34,910
You're still alive.

584
00:33:35,510 --> 00:33:36,430
I'm still alive.

585
00:33:38,820 --> 00:33:39,780
Let me look at you.

586
00:33:50,470 --> 00:33:51,380
What happened to your face?

587
00:33:52,470 --> 00:33:54,190
It's... It's nothing.

588
00:33:59,990 --> 00:34:01,430
I thought

589
00:34:01,430 --> 00:34:03,910
I would never see you again.

590
00:34:12,260 --> 00:34:13,100
Forgive me.

591
00:34:14,660 --> 00:34:16,100
It's my fault.

592
00:34:16,260 --> 00:34:17,310
I should have...

593
00:34:17,580 --> 00:34:19,430
I should have taken you away back then.

594
00:34:19,740 --> 00:34:20,830
I'm sorry.

595
00:34:35,310 --> 00:34:37,470
What happened after you left?

596
00:34:43,740 --> 00:34:45,620
After I delivered the message
for Master,

597
00:34:46,540 --> 00:34:48,620
someone put a sack over my head
and knocked me unconscious.

598
00:34:50,140 --> 00:34:51,220
Come. Throw her here.

599
00:34:55,870 --> 00:34:56,350
Let's go.

600
00:34:57,700 --> 00:34:59,540
When I faintly woke up,

601
00:34:59,910 --> 00:35:01,390
I was already in a mass grave.

602
00:35:02,430 --> 00:35:04,180
They left because they probably thought

603
00:35:04,510 --> 00:35:05,310
I was dead.

604
00:35:06,870 --> 00:35:08,540
After escaping death,
I didn't dare to show my face

605
00:35:09,140 --> 00:35:10,350
or go home.

606
00:35:11,100 --> 00:35:12,310
I was afraid they would catch me.

607
00:35:13,510 --> 00:35:15,260
So I wandered in the neighboring county

608
00:35:15,830 --> 00:35:16,990
for a few months,

609
00:35:17,910 --> 00:35:19,830
eating leftover food.

610
00:35:20,660 --> 00:35:21,910
After a few months,

611
00:35:22,620 --> 00:35:25,100
I returned home to see my brother.

612
00:35:26,180 --> 00:35:30,140
After asking around, I learned
about what happened to the Xue family.

613
00:35:34,350 --> 00:35:34,990
Haitang,

614
00:35:36,740 --> 00:35:37,700
you've suffered.

615
00:35:38,620 --> 00:35:39,620
I failed you.

616
00:35:40,950 --> 00:35:42,910
Madam, you didn't fail me.

617
00:35:43,350 --> 00:35:44,430
It's those who harmed us

618
