621
00:35:50,260 --> 00:35:52,350
I just want you to live.

622
00:35:55,470 --> 00:35:56,470
Get proper rest here.

623
00:35:57,220 --> 00:35:58,430
I'll have someone take good care of you.

624
00:36:11,060 --> 00:36:11,740
Duke Su,

625
00:36:12,350 --> 00:36:13,140
I have a favor to ask.

626
00:36:17,430 --> 00:36:19,100
Is it about the scars on her face?

627
00:36:19,830 --> 00:36:20,430
Yes.

628
00:36:21,620 --> 00:36:22,790
If Jiuyue comes to you,

629
00:36:23,220 --> 00:36:24,620
please inform me.

630
00:36:24,830 --> 00:36:26,950
I want to ask Jiuyue
to treat Magistrate Xue and Haitang.

631
00:36:27,180 --> 00:36:28,950
You know she uses poison, right?

632
00:36:29,310 --> 00:36:30,540
You're risking their lives for survival.

633
00:36:31,260 --> 00:36:31,870
I trust her.

634
00:36:32,220 --> 00:36:33,910
I'll send someone to notify you
when I find her.

635
00:36:40,830 --> 00:36:41,510
Duke Su.

636
00:36:42,350 --> 00:36:42,950
Please come.

637
00:36:43,430 --> 00:36:44,260
Do you know

638
00:36:44,310 --> 00:36:46,540
how to truly protect someone?

639
00:36:47,030 --> 00:36:48,830
Don't push the person
you want to protect away

640
00:36:48,830 --> 00:36:49,830
from you.

641
00:36:50,030 --> 00:36:51,430
Keep her close,

642
00:36:51,790 --> 00:36:53,580
within your sight.

643
00:36:53,700 --> 00:36:54,870
Is that how you do it?

644
00:36:57,060 --> 00:36:57,790
I don't need to.

645
00:36:58,030 --> 00:36:59,620
Duke Su, you just can't stop the habit

646
00:36:59,620 --> 00:37:01,430
of eavesdropping on others, huh?

647
00:37:03,620 --> 00:37:05,790
It's because you speak so loudly.

648
00:37:05,910 --> 00:37:07,790
So now it's my fault?

649
00:37:08,580 --> 00:37:09,510
At least, you realize your mistake.

650
00:37:11,990 --> 00:37:13,830
Are you going to participate
in the selection of the reception envoy

651
00:37:14,140 --> 00:37:14,910
for the Great Zhao delegation?

652
00:37:15,140 --> 00:37:16,430
Why are you bringing this up too?

653
00:37:16,740 --> 00:37:19,030
Shen Yurong is in charge of this matter.

654
00:37:25,140 --> 00:37:25,910
Duke Su,

655
00:37:27,030 --> 00:37:28,700
you once told me

656
00:37:28,830 --> 00:37:30,390
the story
of "Duke Huang of the East Sea."

657
00:37:30,870 --> 00:37:32,180
Today, let me tell you

658
00:37:32,540 --> 00:37:33,830
the story of "A Beauty's Return."

659
00:37:39,220 --> 00:37:41,030
A young nobleman became infatuated

660
00:37:41,260 --> 00:37:43,060
with a beautiful lady
during his travels.

661
00:37:43,470 --> 00:37:44,620
He promised her a lifelong commitment.

662
00:37:45,830 --> 00:37:47,030
But later,

663
00:37:47,350 --> 00:37:49,100
he abandoned her
and returned to the capital.

664
00:37:49,790 --> 00:37:53,620
Under his parents' order, he married
a noblewoman from a prestigious family.

665
00:37:53,700 --> 00:37:54,620
Little did he know,

666
00:37:55,030 --> 00:37:57,390
this woman bore a striking resemblance
to the abandoned lady,

667
00:37:57,510 --> 00:38:00,140
not just in looks
but also in mannerisms.

668
00:38:00,790 --> 00:38:01,700
The nobleman was convinced

669
00:38:02,060 --> 00:38:04,700
that the noble family refused to marry
their real daughter to him.

670
00:38:05,390 --> 00:38:06,580
So they found a substitute bride.

671
00:38:08,350 --> 00:38:11,470
Ironically, the substitute bride
was the abandoned lady.

672
00:38:12,140 --> 00:38:14,140
Throughout their marriage,

673
00:38:14,350 --> 00:38:16,950
the nobleman was consumed
with proving his suspicions.

674
00:38:17,990 --> 00:38:20,950
In the end, guess what happened?

675
00:38:22,830 --> 00:38:24,220
He killed the noblewoman.

676
00:38:25,430 --> 00:38:26,790
Duke Su, why do you enjoy

677
00:38:26,790 --> 00:38:27,990
stories full of bloodshed so much?

678
00:38:28,660 --> 00:38:29,580
Could

679
00:38:31,950 --> 00:38:33,470
they be lovebirds?

680
00:38:36,350 --> 00:38:37,030
Let's wait and see.

681
00:38:54,470 --> 00:38:57,830
I'll perform this show for you.

682
00:39:15,030 --> 00:39:17,140
Why do you think
Jiang Li isn't participating?

683
00:39:17,660 --> 00:39:18,950
Didn't she want to seek guidance

684
00:39:18,950 --> 00:39:20,620
from Shen Yurong before?

685
00:39:21,870 --> 00:39:22,580
Why did you hit me?

686
00:39:22,740 --> 00:39:24,540
You fool. What else could it be?

687
00:39:24,790 --> 00:39:26,310
She must be feeling down.

688
00:39:26,470 --> 00:39:27,910
With so much going on
in your family lately

689
00:39:27,950 --> 00:39:28,910
and Tong gone,

690
00:39:29,060 --> 00:39:30,350
who would have the mood to study

691
00:39:30,350 --> 00:39:31,620
or seek guidance?

692
00:39:31,790 --> 00:39:33,740
People like them who love learning

693
00:39:34,060 --> 00:39:36,220
find it therapeutic.

694
00:39:36,540 --> 00:39:37,620
Don't believe me? Ask Ye Shijie.

695
00:39:39,950 --> 00:39:41,310
Since Jiang Li doesn't want to join,

696
00:39:41,620 --> 00:39:42,620
let's not bring it up anymore.

697
00:39:42,620 --> 00:39:44,030
Let her be in peace.

698
00:39:44,620 --> 00:39:45,790
We shouldn't disturb her either.

699
00:39:45,950 --> 00:39:46,950
We can't do that.

700
00:39:47,430 --> 00:39:48,910
We can't leave her alone either.

701
00:39:49,030 --> 00:39:50,470
Are you discussing
the delegation matters?

702
00:39:51,910 --> 00:39:53,180
What is wrong with you?

703
00:39:53,310 --> 00:39:54,700
- You should've made some noise.
- Li.

704
00:39:54,910 --> 00:39:55,540
Where are you going?

705
00:39:58,100 --> 00:40:00,620
Ye, did His Majesty assign
the delegation matters

706
00:40:01,100 --> 00:40:03,180
to Shen Yurong?

707
00:40:03,540 --> 00:40:03,990
Yes.

708
00:40:08,180 --> 00:40:08,870
I want to join.

709
