728
00:41:47,390 --> 00:41:48,790
Listen to me.

729
00:41:49,140 --> 00:41:50,580
We're able

730
00:41:50,740 --> 00:41:52,990
to enjoy fine food

731
00:41:53,540 --> 00:41:55,220
and comfort life

732
00:41:55,660 --> 00:41:57,430
all because of Eldest Princess.

733
00:41:58,060 --> 00:42:00,350
Before you do anything,

734
00:42:00,660 --> 00:42:02,540
