Eldest Princess.

735
00:42:03,100 --> 00:42:03,790
Do you hear me?

736
00:42:03,910 --> 00:42:05,950
Eldest Princess. Eldest Princess.

737
00:42:06,540 --> 00:42:08,740
It's always about Eldest Princess.

738
00:42:08,950 --> 00:42:12,060
Is the Shen family
Eldest Princess's dog?

739
00:42:13,100 --> 00:42:14,950
What are you saying?

740
00:42:15,390 --> 00:42:16,990
Do you think
everything we have now is given

741
00:42:16,990 --> 00:42:18,470
is given by Eldest Princess?

742
00:42:18,700 --> 00:42:19,700
What about my years

743
00:42:20,100 --> 00:42:22,740
of dedication to the court
and the emperor?

744
00:42:23,390 --> 00:42:24,990
Our daily expenses at the Shen family

745
00:42:24,990 --> 00:42:26,910
are from my hard work,

746
00:42:27,180 --> 00:42:28,580
not from Eldest Princess's rewards!

747
00:42:29,310 --> 00:42:30,620
Mother only cares about you.

748
00:42:30,740 --> 00:42:31,830
She's afraid you might make
the wrong decisions

749
00:42:31,830 --> 00:42:32,830
and make mistakes again.

750
00:42:32,910 --> 00:42:35,430
You remind me day and night like this.

751
00:42:35,510 --> 00:42:39,140
How can I dare to make mistakes?

752
00:42:45,870 --> 00:42:47,660
Yurong will understand your intentions.

753
00:42:56,620 --> 00:42:58,100
The reception envoy selection's
results are out.

754
00:42:58,310 --> 00:42:58,910
