755
00:42:59,540 --> 00:43:00,260
Ye Shijie,

756
00:43:00,390 --> 00:43:01,430
Liu Xu and I have received

757
00:43:01,430 --> 00:43:02,310
our confirmation letters.

758
00:43:02,510 --> 00:43:03,990
