her confirmation letter.

761
00:43:07,060 --> 00:43:08,030
She didn't receive it?

762
00:43:08,540 --> 00:43:10,060
She's the most outstanding among us.

763
00:43:10,060 --> 00:43:10,950
It's impossible not to get selected.

764
00:43:11,350 --> 00:43:11,830
Silly.

765
00:43:12,220 --> 00:43:14,180
