769
00:43:21,830 --> 00:43:22,620
No, it's not possible.

770
00:43:23,510 --> 00:43:25,350
Mr. Shen is probably still deciding.

771
00:43:25,780 --> 00:43:26,580
What do you mean?

772
00:43:27,620 --> 00:43:28,740
I need a favor from you.

773
00:43:29,030 --> 00:43:29,580
What do you need me to do?

774
00:43:30,350 --> 00:43:31,430
I want him to come
to the Jiang's Residence

775
00:43:32,430 --> 00:43:33,350
and personally invite me.

776
00:43:38,460 --> 00:43:39,620
