777
00:43:39,620 --> 00:43:40,180
Your Majesty,

778
00:43:40,620 --> 00:43:43,220
the schedule for the delegation's
reception has been completed.

779
00:43:43,660 --> 00:43:44,510
As for the specific details,

780
00:43:44,830 --> 00:43:46,740
I have requested Serving Officer, Ye Shijie
from the Ministry of Revenue to draft it

781
00:43:46,830 --> 00:43:47,700
into a document.

782
00:43:48,070 --> 00:43:49,220
