this several times.

796
00:44:11,870 --> 00:44:13,740
He has always praised Jiang Li's

797
00:44:13,740 --> 00:44:15,950
"Spring Fading
into White Pear Blossoms."

798
00:44:16,660 --> 00:44:17,950
I wanted her to perform it

799
00:44:18,070 --> 00:44:19,700
at a palace banquet before.

800
00:44:19,990 --> 00:44:21,870
But I had state affairs to attend to

801
00:44:21,990 --> 00:44:22,780
and left early.

802
00:44:23,220 --> 00:44:25,220
During the Entry Exam,
you were also present.

803
00:44:25,660 --> 00:44:26,550
What do you think?

804
00:44:27,700 --> 00:44:28,510
Your Majesty,

805
00:44:29,300 --> 00:44:30,660
it's indeed an excellent piece.

806
00:44:31,580 --> 00:44:33,180
Second Lady Jiang is not among

807
00:44:33,180 --> 00:44:34,220
the confirmed reception envoy.

808
00:44:34,300 --> 00:44:35,700
Did she not submit
a recommendation letter herself?

809
00:44:36,070 --> 00:44:37,870
She did submit one.

810
00:44:38,700 --> 00:44:39,660
But considering

811
00:44:39,940 --> 00:44:41,470
the recent events in the Jiang family,

812
00:44:42,060 --> 00:44:42,910
it wasn't approved yet.

813
00:44:44,180 --> 00:44:46,990
Do you also think an evil spirit
has possessed Second Lady Jiang?

814
00:44:49,100 --> 00:44:50,870
I am aware
of the Jiang family's situation.

815
00:44:51,350 --> 00:44:52,580
However, supernatural matters

816
00:44:52,860 --> 00:44:54,300
are not appropriate for open discussion.

817
00:44:54,580 --> 00:44:56,660
Official Shen,
you're being narrow-minded.

818
00:44:57,100 --> 00:44:57,990
I apologize.

819
00:45:01,020 --> 00:45:01,620
Official Ye,

820
00:45:02,140 --> 00:45:04,220
I will approve Second Lady Jiang's
recommendation letter right away.

821
00:45:04,500 --> 00:45:05,510
As her cousin,

822
00:45:06,100 --> 00:45:07,780
you can pass the letter to her.

823
00:45:08,020 --> 00:45:08,830
Mr. Shen,

824
00:45:09,350 --> 00:45:11,740
this is an official matter.
It wouldn't be proper for me to do it.

825
00:45:12,140 --> 00:45:14,180
Since you didn't approve
her invitation earlier,

826
00:45:14,660 --> 00:45:16,070
Second Lady Jiang
might have misunderstood.

827
00:45:16,830 --> 00:45:17,830
If you don't go,

828
00:45:18,660 --> 00:45:19,910
how can I explain it clearly?

829
00:45:28,260 --> 00:45:30,100
[Govern the People, Serve Heaven]

830
00:45:35,220 --> 00:45:37,030
My Lady, you're truly insightful.

831
00:45:37,260 --> 00:45:38,780
Mr. Shen has indeed come to see you.

832
00:45:39,030 --> 00:45:40,070
He's outside right now.

833
00:45:44,180 --> 00:45:45,260
With the alliance approaching,

834
00:45:45,740 --> 00:45:47,430
[Abundance and Prosperity]
how do you have the time to visit me?

835
00:45:49,580 --> 00:45:52,620
I have a request today.

836
00:45:53,070 --> 00:45:54,550
During the court meeting
about the alliance banquet,

837
00:45:55,260 --> 00:45:59,100
the emperor mentioned he wanted

838
00:45:59,580 --> 00:46:01,180
to hear your "Spring Fading
into White Pear Blossoms."

839
00:46:01,780 --> 00:46:02,830
I played it

840
00:46:03,140 --> 00:46:05,870
at the School of Integrity's Entry Exam.

841
00:46:06,220 --> 00:46:08,180
I didn't expect the emperor
to hold it in such high regard.

842
00:46:08,740 --> 00:46:10,390
Your musical skills are renowned

843
00:46:10,870 --> 00:46:12,220
throughout the capital.

844
00:46:12,700 --> 00:46:13,660
With such fame,

845
00:46:14,100 --> 00:46:15,870
people are bound to talk about it.

846
00:46:15,990 --> 00:46:17,660
It might be best
for you to stay low-key.

847
00:46:17,870 --> 00:46:20,140
"Spring Fading into White Pear Blossoms"
has a sorrowful melody.

848
00:46:20,780 --> 00:46:22,870
With the Great Zhao delegation coming
for the alliance,

849
00:46:23,140 --> 00:46:24,910
playing this might be inappropriate.

850
00:46:25,430 --> 00:46:28,220
So I wish to ask you
to appeal to the emperor

851
00:46:28,510 --> 00:46:29,510
to decline this performance.

852
00:46:30,140 --> 00:46:33,660
[Abundance and Prosperity]
Move with emotion, convince with reason.

853
00:46:34,660 --> 00:46:36,950
Those who don't know better

854
00:46:36,950 --> 00:46:39,910
would think you're very considerate
of me and far-sighted.

855
00:46:40,870 --> 00:46:44,350
I only think you will understand
the situation well,

856
00:46:45,100 --> 00:46:46,740
which is why I came to seek your help.

857
00:46:46,900 --> 00:46:48,380
If you're unwilling,

858
00:46:48,690 --> 00:46:50,330
I will inform the emperor myself

859
00:46:50,420 --> 00:46:51,610
and resign from this task.

860
00:46:53,290 --> 00:46:54,380
Sorry for the trouble today.

861
00:46:55,460 --> 00:46:56,250
I'll take my leave now.

862
00:46:56,260 --> 00:46:58,540
[Abundance and Prosperity]

863
00:46:58,540 --> 00:47:02,130
Mr. Shen, what are you afraid of?

864
00:47:06,460 --> 00:47:08,250
Second Lady Jiang,
what do you mean by this?

865
00:47:08,460 --> 00:47:11,330
If you didn't want me
to join the reception envoy,

866
00:47:11,500 --> 00:47:12,940
you could have just rejected
my application.

867
00:47:13,580 --> 00:47:15,730
But you didn't reject it nor approve it.

868
00:47:16,140 --> 00:47:18,100
You hesitated.

869
00:47:18,780 --> 00:47:19,950
You should know

870
00:47:20,580 --> 00:47:21,740
why I am hesitating.

871
00:47:21,910 --> 00:47:23,910
After all,
your intentions are too obvious.

872
00:47:24,030 --> 00:47:24,950
My intentions?

873
00:47:25,550 --> 00:47:27,180
Have you misunderstood something?

874
00:47:27,350 --> 00:47:28,350
You can fool others.

875
00:47:28,780 --> 00:47:29,740
But not me.

876
00:47:30,140 --> 00:47:32,220
Oh, Mr. Shen.

877
00:47:32,510 --> 00:47:34,140
Should I call you foolish

878
00:47:34,580 --> 00:47:35,870
or self-deluded?

879
00:47:36,780 --> 00:47:37,910
[Abundance and Prosperity]
It seems you still see me

880
00:47:38,780 --> 00:47:40,990
as your late wife.

881
00:47:42,180 --> 00:47:43,470
Since you're so certain,

882
00:47:43,830 --> 00:47:45,220
why did you oppose Eldest Princess

883
00:47:45,220 --> 00:47:46,740
before the emperor?

884
00:47:48,700 --> 00:47:50,580
You should know best

885
00:47:51,870 --> 00:47:57,550
that I am the Secretariat Director
and Grand Preceptor's daughter,

886
00:47:58,510 --> 00:48:00,430
not your infamous late wife.

887
00:48:00,950 --> 00:48:02,620
Even if I do look like her,

888
00:48:02,620 --> 00:48:03,430
so what?

889
00:48:04,430 --> 00:48:05,580
In that case,

890
00:48:07,180 --> 00:48:09,740
why do you insist on joining
the reception envoy I manage?

891
00:48:10,140 --> 00:48:12,580
My maid died protecting me.

892
00:48:13,620 --> 00:48:14,990
She was like a sister to me.

893
00:48:15,620 --> 00:48:17,470
I am sad and heartbroken.

894
00:48:17,620 --> 00:48:18,910
I have been in despair for days.

895
00:48:19,220 --> 00:48:20,070
I just want to enjoy

896
00:48:20,070 --> 00:48:22,220
the lively atmosphere
of the alliance banquet.

897
00:48:23,070 --> 00:48:23,910
Is that wrong?

898
00:48:24,510 --> 00:48:27,300
If you insist
on rejecting my application,

899
00:48:27,830 --> 00:48:30,070
please do not impose your feelings

900
00:48:30,070 --> 00:48:31,220
for your late wife on me.

901
00:48:31,780 --> 00:48:32,740
Instead,

902
00:48:32,740 --> 00:48:34,180
find a more convincing reason.

903
00:48:35,070 --> 00:48:36,260
Otherwise, people might think

904
00:48:36,950 --> 00:48:38,510
you have a guilty conscience.

905
00:48:43,300 --> 00:48:45,430
You should leave now, Mr. Shen.

906
00:49:41,300 --> 00:49:42,140
Son,

907
00:49:42,660 --> 00:49:44,220
listen to me.

908
00:49:44,870 --> 00:49:46,140
Our family

909
00:49:46,140 --> 00:49:48,390
can enjoy such fine food

910
00:49:48,830 --> 00:49:50,620
and comfort life

911
00:49:51,070 --> 00:49:52,660
all thanks to Eldest Princess.

912
00:49:53,030 --> 00:49:55,220
The way you speak pains me.

913
00:49:55,990 --> 00:49:58,430
But unfortunately,
I can't comfort you now.

914
00:49:59,550 --> 00:50:01,580
My maid died protecting me.

915
00:50:02,350 --> 00:50:03,700
She was like a sister to me.

916
00:50:04,260 --> 00:50:04,950
I just want to enjoy

917
00:50:04,950 --> 00:50:07,260
the lively atmosphere
of the alliance banquet.

918
00:50:34,500 --> 00:50:39,980
♪If there are no happy memories♪

919
00:50:42,100 --> 00:50:47,580
♪How can we traverse
the forbidden land of sorrow?♪

920
00:50:49,380 --> 00:50:55,460
♪Two cold and unfeeling bodies♪

921
00:50:56,140 --> 00:51:03,420
♪Holding hands,
can we get through the snow season?♪

922
00:51:04,460 --> 00:51:10,940
♪In the cold wind, in the long night♪

923
00:51:11,740 --> 00:51:18,020
♪Embracing the remaining warmth♪

924
00:51:19,300 --> 00:51:26,540
♪The depth of the sea, unfathomable♪

925
00:51:26,620 --> 00:51:32,620
♪Can it bury yesterday's sighs?♪

926
00:51:33,300 --> 00:51:39,340
♪Continue to love,
cherishing it with my life♪

927
00:51:41,180 --> 00:51:47,900
♪Continue to live,
even with only a glimmer of hope♪

928
00:51:49,020 --> 00:51:55,820
♪Whether in sorrow or joy,
I believe in you♪

929
00:51:56,820 --> 00:52:02,740
♪I'd rather be trapped
in the world's extremes♪

930
00:52:03,460 --> 00:52:10,580
♪Continue to live,
exhausting all courage♪

931
00:52:10,820 --> 00:52:18,100
♪Continue to love,
until the breath runs out♪

932
00:52:18,980 --> 00:52:25,780
♪Traversing half a lifetime
of loneliness, just to meet you♪

933
00:52:26,380 --> 00:52:32,820
♪After the hardships,
never to part again♪

